00:02:05.290 --> 00:02:07.520
the interviewer doesn't have--
oh, you know, I mean to.

00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:08.460
I'm going to get to it.

00:02:08.460 --> 00:02:09.585
DANA HAN-KLEIN: I loved it.

