I don't think you can
cure every cancer.

01:02:28.110 --> 01:02:30.520
There's some failure
modes out there.

01:02:30.520 --> 01:02:33.560
And then I'd like you to invent
a better battery, the water

01:02:33.560 --> 01:02:34.660
desalinization.

01:02:34.660 --> 01:02:36.670
I would like you to raise
the standard of living

01:02:36.670 --> 01:02:39.550
